{"tid":1849522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拿口罩點生產都一定唔夠貨，用遮陽帽或者類似既野頂住得唔得先？","createTime":"2020-01-29T06:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T10:19:03.000Z","uid":28068,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6563cf246279a6cd302cab9f778c42b027e86baf","tid":1849522,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:03:35.000Z","msg":"遮陽帽 / 頭盔 / 面罩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之有塊野係前面擋住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>雖然都係過濾唔到空氣漂浮過黎個d<br />\n<br />\n但直飛入眼同口鼻既都擋到大部分</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n同埋有個好處係可以用循環再用<br />\n消毒酒精抺一抺又用得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿口罩計晒成個東南亞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">依家每日起碼消耗十億個</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你全球點生產都好<br />\n一定唔夠用既速度快<br />\n一個月內一定有人無晒無罩用<br />\n我建議大家諗定無口罩時用咩代替<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有張相係個大陸人用水樽笠住個頭<br />\n雖然好笑但都叫有用架<br />\n難保一個月後香港人會唔會學佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fa9978ba616e41b1fc1d559fcbeffb3d653fe7","tid":1849522,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6563cf246279a6cd302cab9f778c42b027e86baf","tid":1849522,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:03:35.000Z","msg":"遮陽帽 / 頭盔 / 面罩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之有塊野係前面擋住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>雖然都係